events.text: oh, hello there [PlayerName]. we finally got to our ninth life, did we? congratulations! well, to you and to me. to both of us.
since we are the same cat.
oh, you know how it works. cat law, or whatever.
i have to say, as far as deaths go, mine wasn’t so bad.
a little unconventional, but not bad.
how was i supposed to know that other cat had massive claws? it’s unnatural. messed up.
*sigh* well, you know what they say. live fast, die young, or whatever.
we probably should’ve picked our battles more carefully, huh?
c’mon, [PlayerName]. let’s move on up in the world.
